{"id":181763,"date":"2023-07-26T15:42:27","date_gmt":"2023-07-26T10:12:27","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/?p=181763"},"modified":"2023-08-11T09:53:18","modified_gmt":"2023-08-11T04:23:18","slug":"ravi-sihag","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/ravi-sihag\/","title":{"rendered":"Ravi Sihag (IAS) Wiki, Age, Wife, Family, Biography &amp; More"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Sihag-Picture.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-181774\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Sihag-Picture.jpg\" alt=\"Ravi Sihag\" width=\"445\" height=\"467\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Sihag-Picture.jpg 417w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Sihag-Picture-286x300.jpg 286w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 445px) 100vw, 445px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>Ravi Sihag is an Indian Administration Service Officer of the 2021 batch of the Madhya Pradesh cadre. He achieved the 18th rank in the UPSC CSE 2021 examination on his fourth attempt. He was also the top scorer among all the candidates who appeared for the exam in Hindi medium. Before this accomplishment, Ravi had previously cracked the exam twice, securing the 337th rank in 2018 and the 317th rank in 2019. In those attempts, he was assigned to the Indian Defense Accounts Service (IDAS) and the Indian Railway Traffic Service (IRTS), respectively.<\/p>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_62 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-custom ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">Contents<\/p>\n<label for=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-item-65bce3c4add51\" class=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-label\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" 