ddress\">Address<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/ravi-sihag\/#Signature\" title=\"Signature\">Signature<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/ravi-sihag\/#Career\" title=\"Career\">Career<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/ravi-sihag\/#FactsTrivia\" title=\"Facts\/Trivia\">Facts\/Trivia<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"WikiBiography\"><\/span>Wiki\/Biography<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Ravi Kumar Sihag was born on Thursday, 2 November 1995<strong> (age 28 Years; as of 2023)<\/strong> in Village Chak 3 Bam, Vijayanagar, Sri Ganganagar, Rajasthan. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_181763_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_181763_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_181763_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_181763_1_1\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[1]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_181763_1_1\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/ravisihag01\/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Ravi Kumar Sihag&#8217;s Instagram Account<\/a><\/span><\/span>\u00a0His zodiac sign is Scorpio. He completed his school education up to 7th class at Saraswati Vidya Mandir School, Sri Ganganagar, Rajasthan. He then joined Sharda School in Anupgarh to complete his schooling up to 11th Grade. He completed his 12th class at a Government senior secondary school in Vijayanagar, Rajasthan. In 2015, he attained a bachelor&#8217;s degree in arts from Sharda College, Anupgarh, Rajasthan. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_181763_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_181763_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_181763_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_181763_1_2\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[2]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_181763_1_2\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.dnaindia.com\/education\/report-ias-ravi-sihag-farmer-s-son-who-cleared-upsc-3-times-becomes-ias-in-4th-attempt-with-air-18-civil-services-3037354\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">DNA<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Physical_Appearance\"><\/span>Physical Appearance<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>Height (approx.):<\/strong> 5&#8242; 8&#8243;<\/p>\n<p><strong>Hair Colour: <\/strong>Black<\/p>\n<p><strong>Eye Colour: <\/strong>Black<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Sihag-Image.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-181773\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Sihag-Image.jpg\" alt=\"Ravi Sihag\" width=\"364\" height=\"486\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Sihag-Image.jpg 466w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Sihag-Image-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 364px) 100vw, 364px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Family\"><\/span>Family<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<div>He belongs to an Economically Weaker Section family.<\/div>\n<div><\/div>\n<div id=\"attachment_181766\" style=\"width: 491px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Kumar-Sihags-caste-in-IAS-ranking-list.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-181766\" class=\" wp-image-181766\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Kumar-Sihags-caste-in-IAS-ranking-list.jpg\" alt=\"Ravi Kumar Sihag's caste in IAS ranking list\" width=\"481\" height=\"189\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Kumar-Sihags-caste-in-IAS-ranking-list.jpg 822w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Kumar-Sihags-caste-in-IAS-ranking-list-300x118.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Kumar-Sihags-caste-in-IAS-ranking-list-768x302.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 481px) 100vw, 481px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-181766\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ravi Kumar Sihag&#8217;s caste in the IAS ranking list<\/p><\/div>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Parents_Siblings\"><\/span><strong>Parents &amp; Siblings<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>His father, Ramkumar Sihag, is a farmer. His mother, Vimala Devi, is a housewife.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_181770\" style=\"width: 397px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Sihag-with-his-father-and-mother.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-181770\" class=\"size-full wp-image-181770\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Sihag-with-his-father-and-mother.jpg\" alt=\"Ravi Sihag with his father and mother\" width=\"387\" height=\"347\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Sihag-with-his-father-and-mother.jpg 387w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Sihag-with-his-father-and-mother-300x269.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 387px) 100vw, 387px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-181770\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ravi Sihag with his father and mother<\/p><\/div>\n<p>He has three elder sisters named Poonam Sihag (housewife), Raveena Sihag (teacher), and Komal Sihag (Anganwadi supervisor).<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_181771\" style=\"width: 397px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Kumar-Sihag-with-his-sisters.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-181771\" class=\"size-full wp-image-181771\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Kumar-Sihag-with-his-sisters.jpg\" alt=\"Ravi Kumar Sihag with his sisters\" width=\"387\" height=\"337\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Kumar-Sihag-with-his-sisters.jpg 387w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Kumar-Sihag-with-his-sisters-300x261.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 387px) 100vw, 387px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-181771\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ravi Kumar Sihag with his sisters<\/p><\/div>\n<div id=\"attachment_181772\" style=\"width: 407px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Sihag-with-his-sisters.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-181772\" class=\"size-full wp-image-181772\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Sihag-with-his-sisters.jpg\" alt=\"Ravi Sihag with his sisters\" width=\"397\" height=\"337\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Sihag-with-his-sisters.jpg 397w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Sihag-with-his-sisters-300x255.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 397px) 100vw, 397px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-181772\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ravi Sihag with his sisters<\/p><\/div>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Wife\"><\/span><strong>Wife <\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>He is unmarried.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Address\"><\/span>Address<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>C\/o Ramkumar Sihag, village Chak 3 Bam, Vijayanagar, Sri Ganganagar, Rajasthan, 335704<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Signature\"><\/span>Signature<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<div id=\"attachment_181765\" style=\"width: 302px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Kumar-Sihags-signature.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-181765\" class=\"size-full wp-image-181765\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Kumar-Sihags-signature.jpg\" alt=\"Ravi Kumar Sihag's signature\" width=\"292\" height=\"163\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-181765\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ravi Kumar Sihag&#8217;s signature<\/p><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Career\"><\/span>Career<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Ravi attempted the UPSC exam for the first time in 2018 and achieved 337th rank and was selected for the Indian Defense Accounts Service (IDAS). In 2019, in his second attempt, he secured 317th rank and was selected for the Indian Railway Traffic Service (IRTS). However, Ravi Kumar had a strong desire to become an IAS officer, so he continued his preparation for\u00a0the civil service examinations even after clearing the exam twice. In 2020, on his third attempt, he couldn&#8217;t pass the UPSC preliminary exams. However, in 2021, he succeeded in the exam with an All India Rank (AIR) of 18 on his fourth try, and as a result, he was appointed as an IAS officer.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_181778\" style=\"width: 487px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Kumar-Sihag-while-attending-the-felicitation-programme-for-UPSC-toppers-at-DoPT-by-Honble-MoS-PP-in-2022.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-181778\" class=\" wp-image-181778\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Kumar-Sihag-while-attending-the-felicitation-programme-for-UPSC-toppers-at-DoPT-by-Honble-MoS-PP-in-2022.jpg\" alt=\"Ravi Kumar Sihag while attending the felicitation programme for UPSC toppers at DoPT by Hon\u2019ble MoS (PP) in 2022\" width=\"477\" height=\"321\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Kumar-Sihag-while-attending-the-felicitation-programme-for-UPSC-toppers-at-DoPT-by-Honble-MoS-PP-in-2022.jpg 617w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Kumar-Sihag-while-attending-the-felicitation-programme-for-UPSC-toppers-at-DoPT-by-Honble-MoS-PP-in-2022-300x202.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 477px) 100vw, 477px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-181778\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ravi Kumar Sihag while attending the felicitation programme for UPSC toppers at DoPT by Hon\u2019ble MoS (PP) in 2022<\/p><\/div>\n<p>In the UPSC exam 2021, the top 17 candidates were from the English medium. However, Ravi Kumar Sihag, who appeared for the exam in Hindi medium, secured the 18th rank, making him the highest-ranking candidate among all the Hindi medium students in UPSC CSE 2021. Ravi&#8217;s main subjects in the UPSC examination were Political Science, Economics, and English Literature, and he chose Hindi Literature as an optional subject.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_181782\" style=\"width: 452px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/The-UPSC-marksheet-of-Ravi-Sihag.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-181782\" class=\" wp-image-181782\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/The-UPSC-marksheet-of-Ravi-Sihag.jpg\" alt=\"The UPSC marksheet of Ravi Sihag\" width=\"442\" height=\"376\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/The-UPSC-marksheet-of-Ravi-Sihag.jpg 583w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/The-UPSC-marksheet-of-Ravi-Sihag-300x255.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 442px) 100vw, 442px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-181782\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">The UPSC mark sheet of Ravi Sihag<\/p><\/div>\n<p>On 30 August 2023, Ravi Kumar Sihag began his training at the Lal Bahadur Shastri National Academy of Administration (LBSNAA) in Mussoorie, Uttarakhand. During the training, he participated in and won a quiz about the &#8216;Constitution and Life of Dr Ambedkar&#8217; that was organized on the occasion of Dr Ambedkar Jayanti. For his victory, he was honoured with a prize by the fourteenth President of India <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/ram-nath-kovind\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Ram Nath Kovind<\/a> and the Governor of Uttarakhand, Gurmit Singh.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_181784\" style=\"width: 492px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/ravi-Kumar-Sihag-while-receving-a-prize-from-the-Honble-Ram-Nath-Kovind-and-the-Governor-of-Uttarakhand-Gurmit-Singh-in-April-2023.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-181784\" class=\" wp-image-181784\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/ravi-Kumar-Sihag-while-receving-a-prize-from-the-Honble-Ram-Nath-Kovind-and-the-Governor-of-Uttarakhand-Gurmit-Singh-in-April-2023.jpg\" alt=\"Ravi Kumar Sihag while receving a prize from the Hon'ble Ram Nath Kovind and the Governor of Uttarakhand, Gurmit Singh in April 2023\" width=\"482\" height=\"350\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/ravi-Kumar-Sihag-while-receving-a-prize-from-the-Honble-Ram-Nath-Kovind-and-the-Governor-of-Uttarakhand-Gurmit-Singh-in-April-2023.jpg 657w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/ravi-Kumar-Sihag-while-receving-a-prize-from-the-Honble-Ram-Nath-Kovind-and-the-Governor-of-Uttarakhand-Gurmit-Singh-in-April-2023-300x218.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 482px) 100vw, 482px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-181784\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ravi Kumar Sihag (left) while receiving a prize from the Hon&#8217;ble Ram Nath Kovind (right) and the Governor of Uttarakhand, Gurmit Singh (middle) in April 2023<\/p><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"FactsTrivia\"><\/span>Facts\/Trivia<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Before starting his preparation for the UPSC exams in 2017, Ravi Kumar used to help his father in the fields until he finished his graduation.\n<p><div id=\"attachment_181779\" style=\"width: 483px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Kumar-Sihag-while-farming-at-his-homwtown.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-181779\" class=\" wp-image-181779\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Kumar-Sihag-while-farming-at-his-homwtown.jpg\" alt=\"Ravi Kumar Sihag while farming at his home town\" width=\"473\" height=\"370\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Kumar-Sihag-while-farming-at-his-homwtown.jpg 565w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Kumar-Sihag-while-farming-at-his-homwtown-300x235.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 473px) 100vw, 473px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-181779\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ravi Kumar Sihag while farming in the fields in his home town<\/p><\/div><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>During his free time, Ravi Kumar Sihag enjoys travelling to far-off destinations and working out at the gym. He frequently shares pictures of his gym sessions on social media.\n<p><div id=\"attachment_181787\" style=\"width: 422px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Kumar-Sihag-during-his-vacations.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-181787\" class=\" wp-image-181787\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Kumar-Sihag-during-his-vacations.jpg\" alt=\"Ravi Kumar Sihag during his vacations\" width=\"412\" height=\"470\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Kumar-Sihag-during-his-vacations.jpg 536w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Ravi-Kumar-Sihag-during-his-vacations-263x300.jpg 263w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 412px) 100vw, 412px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-181787\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ravi Kumar Sihag during his vacations<\/p><\/div><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div class=\"489bcfb86580b123547338c91db0eff2\" data-index=\"3\" style=\"float: none; margin:3px 0 3px 0; text-align:center;\">\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\"\r\n     style=\"display:block\"\r\n     data-ad-format=\"autorelaxed\"\r\n     data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6769524711517462\"\r\n     data-ad-slot=\"2473600074\"><\/ins>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size: 0px; height: 0px; line-height: 0px; margin: 0; padding: 0; clear: both;\"><\/div><div class=\"speaker-mute footnotes_reference_container\"> <div class=\"footnote_container_prepare\"><p><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" id=\"footnotes_container_label_expand_181763_1\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_label pointer\" on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_181763_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_plus_181763_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_minus_181763_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed)\">References<\/span><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" id=\"footnotes_container_button_plus_181763_1\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_collapse_button\" on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_181763_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_plus_181763_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_minus_181763_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed)\">[+]<\/span><span><\/span><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" id=\"footnotes_container_button_minus_181763_1\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_collapse_button collapsed\" on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_181763_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_plus_181763_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_butto